# No Sleep Web App Built

The single-page web app has been successfully built and placed in the Sagesleeper directory on your Desktop.

## Features Implemented
- **Screen Wake Lock**: Uses the native browser `navigator.wakeLock.request('screen')` API to keep your screen continuously awake.
- **Micro-Animations & UI**: Styled with modern CSS "glassmorphism", dynamic rotating background glows, and toggle-state animations for physical feedback.
- **Live Clock**: Shows the exact current time and date so the app is useful even while resting on a monitor.
- **Re-acquire behavior**: Automatically reacquires the lock if you switch tabs, minimize, and reopen the tab if it was previously locked.

