## How to use
Simply double-click [index.html](file:///C:/Users/ChinonsoNnodebe/OneDrive%20-%20Globus%20Bank%20Limited/Desktop/Sagesleeper/index.html) to open it in your daily web browser (Edge, Chrome, or Firefox). Click the central **"Enable Wake Lock"** button. The color indicator will turn from purple to green, and your screen will stay awake indefinitely until you disable the lock or close the page!
